sequenceDiagram
  participant Orchestrator
  participant API
  participant DB
  participant Worker

  Orchestrator->>API: GET /health/live
  API-->>Orchestrator: 200 {status: "ok"}

  Orchestrator->>API: GET /health/ready
  API->>DB: select 1 (when postgres mode)
  DB-->>API: ok
  API-->>Orchestrator: 200 {status: "ok", checks:{database:"ok"}}

  Note over Worker: scheduled report batch
  Orchestrator->>Worker: run report-worker (daily/weekly/monthly/yearly)
  Worker->>API: execute SendDueReports
  API-->>Worker: sent/skipped/failed
  alt failed > 0
    Worker-->>Orchestrator: exit code 1
  else failed = 0
    Worker-->>Orchestrator: exit code 0
  end

